sequenceDiagram
    participant AppContainer as Web Application
    participant DockerDaemon as Local Docker Socket
    participant Monitor as Reliability Engine (API)
    participant AIEngine as AI Diagnostic Module (Phi-3)
    participant DB as SQLite Datastore
    participant Frontend as React Dashboard

    loop Continuous Telemetry Interval (e.g., 60s)
        Monitor->>DockerDaemon: Poll `docker inspect` for Status
        DockerDaemon-->>Monitor: Returns Metrics (RestartCount, CPU, Mem, Health)
        
        alt RestartCount > Threshold (Crash Loop Detected)
            Monitor->>DockerDaemon: Block restart and Halt Container
            Note over Monitor,DockerDaemon: Halting prevents Resource Exhaustion
            
            Monitor->>DockerDaemon: Extract latest 1,000 lines of `stderr/stdout`
            DockerDaemon-->>Monitor: Raw Crash Logs & Stack Trace
            
            Monitor->>AIEngine: Pipe Raw Logs + Diagnostic Prompt Context
            Note over AIEngine: Local LLM processes text to find exceptions
            
            AIEngine-->>Monitor: Return structured semantic Fix (JSON)
            
            Monitor->>DB: Update App Status to 'Crash Loop'
            Monitor->>DB: Save AI Root-Cause Diagnostic Analysis
            
            Monitor->>Frontend: Broadcast SSE (Server-Sent Event) Update
            Frontend-->>User: Display AI Fix Recommendation Modal
        else Normal Operation
            Monitor->>DB: Update Heartbeat Timestamp (OK)
        end
    end
